OL,3,CActor Micheal Ward bailed after
OL,4,Cappearing in court charged with rape
OL,6,FBafta-winning actor Micheal Ward has
OL,7,Fbeen bailed after appearing in court
OL,8,Fcharged with rape and sexual assault.
OL,10,FThe 27-year-old, who has starred in
OL,11,FBlue Story and Top Boy, is accused of
OL,12,Ftwo counts of rape and three counts of
OL,13,Fsexual assault.
OL,15,FWard appeared at Thames Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt on Thursday where he spoke to
OL,17,Fconfirm his name, address and date of
OL,18,Fbirth during a short hearing.
