OL,3,CActor Micheal Ward bailed after
OL,4,Cappearing in court charged with rape
OL,6,FHe did not enter any pleas and was
OL,7,Fgranted conditional bail to next
OL,8,Fappear at Snaresbrook Crown Court on
OL,9,FSeptember 25.
OL,11,FHis condition is not to contact the
OL,12,Falleged victim.
OL,14,FIn a statement issued after the
OL,15,Fcharges were announced last month,
OL,16,FWard said: "I deny the charges against
OL,17,Fme entirely," and he added he had co-
OL,18,Foperated with police throughout their
OL,19,Finvestigation.
