OL,6,FThe Jamaican-born actor was awarded
OL,7,Fthe Bafta rising star honour in 2020
OL,8,Fand was nominated for the best
OL,9,Fsupporting actor Bafta for his role in
OL,10,FBBC's Small Axe in 2021 and the 2022
OL,11,Ffilm Empire Of Light.
OL,13,FWard played in the Soccer Aid match at
OL,14,FStamford Bridge last year and gave a
OL,15,Freading at the Christmas Eve carol
OL,16,Fservice hosted by the Princess of
OL,17,FWales in 2023.
